  <brief_title>The Role of Microparticles as a Biomarker</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Microparticles as a Biomarker in Distinguishing Between Thrombotic Thrombocytopenic Purpura (TTP) and Atypical Hemolytic Uremic Syndrome (aHUS)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
